==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Objectize
<hw>Ob"ject*ize</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To make an
object of; to regard as an object; to place in the position of an
object.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>In the latter, as <qex>objectized</qex> by the former, arise the
emotions and affections.</q> <rj><qau>Coleridge.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Objectless</ent>⟦br⟧
